   <body>
      <context>
         <p>You will need to obtain the following files from your Apttus contact.</p>
         <ul>
            <li>Apttus.XAuthor.AppManifest.xml – The add-in manifest file</li>
            <li>WindowsOfficeAddInsLauncher.exe – The add-in utility required for completing
               Windows installation</li>
         </ul>
      </context>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Save the manifest file Apttus.XAuthor.AppManifest.xml to a location on your
               computer. Make a note of the file path.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Run the WindowsOfficeAddInsLauncher.exe file.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Enter the complete file path that points to the manifest file on your system (for
               example, C:\OfficeManifest\Apttus.XAuthor.AppManifest.xml) and press Enter. </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Close the utility window.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Open Microsoft Word and go to <menucascade>
                  <uicontrol>File</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Options</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Trust Center </uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Trust Center Settings</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Trust Add-in Catalogs</uicontrol>
               </menucascade>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Highlight the Office manifest file catalog entry and click
                  <uicontrol>Remove</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Close all open Microsoft Word instances.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Open Microsoft Word and go to <menucascade>
                  <uicontrol>File</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Options</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Trust Center </uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Trust Center Settings</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Trust Add-in Catalogs</uicontrol>
               </menucascade>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In the Category Url field, add the appropriate catalog path for your add-in, make sure <uicontrol>Show in Menu</uicontrol> is checked, and click <uicontrol>OK</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Close Microsoft Word.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Open Microsoft Word and go to <menucascade>
                  <uicontrol>Insert</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>My Add-ins</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>X-Author Contracts</uicontrol>
               </menucascade> to run the add-in.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
